It sounds like you&#39;re probably looking for Fragments. These will let you return multiple elements without having to wrap them in a div etc:

https://reactjs.org/docs/fragments.html

    render() {
      return (
        &lt;React.Fragment&gt;
          &lt;ChildA /&gt;
          &lt;ChildB /&gt;
          &lt;ChildC /&gt;
        &lt;/React.Fragment&gt;
      );
    }

You can also use empty angled brackets as shorthand for these:

    render() {
      return (
        &lt;&gt;
          &lt;ChildA /&gt;
          &lt;ChildB /&gt;
          &lt;ChildC /&gt;
        &lt;/&gt;
      );
    }

